{"tid":801716,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國反情報官員：支那利用社交網站「領英」LinkedIn招攬間諜","createTime":"2018-09-01T01:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T05:42:59.000Z","uid":79563,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"622f9627bdafffe85db08e2dc986331d1af36e1b","tid":801716,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T01:36:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=1027807\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_367%26itemid%3D1027807&d=cHFr5T%2F05JVuldNlAwFIBfjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=dae7f481\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=1027807</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://bnextmedia.s3.hicloud.net.tw/image/album/2016-10/img-1476162072-80483.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbnextmedia.s3.hicloud.net.tw%2Fimage%2Falbum%2F2016-10%2Fimg-1476162072-80483.jpg&h=bca2a669&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國反情報官員表示，中國的間諜機構利用專業人士使用的社交網站「領英」LinkedIn上的虛假賬號，試圖招攬可以接觸到政府及商業機密的美國人，要求「領英」關閉有關賬號。中方否認指控，批評是別有用心。<br />\n<br />\n「領英」在全球二百多個國家及地區，擁有五億七千多萬用戶，當中超過一億五千萬個在美國。報道指，被接觸的用戶中，很多是美國政府僱員，亦有在私營企業任職的人士，當中主要是高科技、醫療衛生或綠色能源等領域的專家。在去年十二月，德國情報機構警告，中方利用假冒的「領英」帳號，收集德國官員的信息，試圖招攬至少一萬名德國官員和政客。英國情報當局亦曾發出類似警告。"},{"pid":"65173f3b372cc41d70870471458fbd29a2a81a1b","tid":801716,"uid":131691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T01:59:40.000Z","msg":"尋日啱啱Reuters見到<br />\n今日有人譯咗<br />\n<br />\n其實LinkedIn真係比Facebook仲恐怖，你基本上將成個履歷公諸於世...<br />\n（當然，對起底好有用）"},{"pid":"0c5789b479a0cb27695a4a57cb87ae374ced5e58","tid":801716,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:05:49.000Z","msg":"免費資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6f919735e8560fcc8c025912ebebf1831785ff","tid":801716,"uid":131691,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:06:38.000Z","msg":"講多啲details，因為881903個報導唔齊全<br />\n支那用LinkedIn所招攬嘅「間諜」未必係平時大家睇戲嗰種自願出賣國家嘅間諜<br />\n佢嘅方法好多時係邀請外國持有某專業技術/知識嘅人，去支那出席某啲活動，途中就跟蹤，影相，製造緋聞證據，blackmail個人去幫中共做間諜。<br />\n<br />\n詳情可以睇返Reuters個報道，有片，個counter-intelligence事頭親自講解：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-linkedin-china-espionage-exclusive/exclusive-us-accuses-china-of-super-aggressive-spy-campaign-on-linkedin-idUSKCN1LG15Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-linkedin-china-espionage-exclusive%2Fexclusive-us-accuses-china-of-super-aggressive-spy-campaign-on-linkedin-idUSKCN1LG15Y&d=cHFr5T%2F05JVuldNlAwFIBfjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=3187eef8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-linkedin-china-espionage-exclusive%2Fexclusive-us-accuses-china-of-super-aggressive-spy-campaign-on-linkedin-idUSKCN1LG15Y&h=868e537d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-linkedin-china-espionage-exclusive/exclusive-us-accuses-china-of-super-aggressive-spy-campaign-on-linkedin-idUSKCN1LG15Y</a>"},{"pid":"5a0a147d6f6552841503ba9f42bbad99f87c7519","tid":801716,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:07:20.000Z","msg":"睇錯 Lihkg"},{"pid":"b2333670e6870740667d55b9d6ce5550de4e3aba","tid":801716,"uid":64191,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:13:15.000Z","msg":"中國仲擅長用美人計引誘外國人<br />\n所以話⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4703a2db5fe9f74115d163a4d51debb7e9c9f16c","tid":801716,"uid":52459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T02:21:51.000Z","msg":"其實擺資料上linkin真係會多人被刮角嗎？我都經常用linkin起人底，都唔明放咁多個人資料去做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9243a96cce1b05b49df146b1450c237b575a96af","tid":801716,"uid":25424,"like":1,"disli